<div class="row">
  <br><br><br>
  <div class="medium-8 medium-centered column">
    <p>I look forward to speaking with you. Please answer three questions, then you will be taken to the calendar to schedule a conversation. â€“ Dr. Fletcher</p>
  </div>
  <form >
    <div class="medium-8 medium-centered column">
        <form>
            <label>Name:
              <input ng-model="client.name" type="text" >
            </label>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
      <label>Where are you now with your health?</label>
      <textarea  ng-model="client.past" cols="30" rows="6"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
      <label>Where would you like to be?</label>
      <textarea ng-model="client.future"  cols="30" rows="6"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered">
      <label>How can I help you get there?</label>
      <textarea ng-model="client.help"  cols="30" rows="6"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="medium-8 column medium-centered" style="text-align: center;">
      <button type="submit" ng-click="sendClientEmail(client)" />Take me to Calendar</button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>